      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/fanxiaofang/obsidian-murmur/compare/0.4.2...0.4.3\r\n\r\n### Script element (if ever flagged)\r\nReact 19's internal preinitScript() / preinitModuleScript() contain document.createElement(\"script\") dead code paths. This plugin never renders <script> elements or calls preinit APIs, so these paths are unreachable. A Vite plugin strips these during build to avoid false positives in the static scanner.\r\n\r\n### Vault Enumeration\r\nThe plugin calls getMarkdownFiles() only to get file paths, then immediately filters for files inside the daily notes folder. It reads no file names and never touches content outside that folder. This is the only API to list all markdown files in a vault, and is standard practice used by Dataview, Calendar, Todoist, etc",
